# Project

This is a browser-based 3D world engine — not a one-off game or demo scene.

## Stack

- React
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Three.js
- React Three Fiber
- Drei

## Vision

Build reusable, data-driven 3D environments that can be extended over many years.

The first environment is a walkable version of the owner's real house.

We are building an **engine**, not just a game. The project should evolve toward:

- Reusable world generation
- Player interactions
- Multiplayer
- AI characters and behaviors

## Core constraint

Do not manually model entire environments in JSX.

Worlds should be described through data structures and generated from reusable components.

Treat one Three.js unit as roughly one foot.
